感觉精力不够用。目前刚考完综合阶段考试，如果考试顺利拿到证书，继续选择进入事务所过于理想化吗？如果较大的事务所不收，打算找小所拿 1 年经验再跳大所。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-7579dd073f990f5777ec3bdb9994f980_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "30 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/551857320"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Ih4PG5bfj1+wpEAMaCDg0OTE4MzkyINih1ZgGMAA4J0Adcgk1NTE4NTczMjB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "30_1662733009.457547", "card_id": "Q_311752133", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 26542}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有什么话想送给一事无成的年轻人？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "生活很累，你很棒！"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-034f12040a54ef0dc04d4668009d18fe_hd.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "30 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/311752133"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIh4PG5bfj1+wpEAMaCDMxNTU0OTcxIIHZ/+IFMJ0BOM3MBEAecgkzMTE3NTIxMzN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "31_1662733009.4581335", "card_id": "Q_552026110", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 140}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "Java 里的继承是否要遵守《民法典》？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-8d880291a64c1473120677c0d01c4cca_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "30 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/552026110"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ih4PG5bfj1+wpEAMaCDg0OTU1OTExIMyw25gGMBQ46AJAH3IJNTUyMDI2MTEweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "32_1662733009.4586668", "card_id": "Q_